    public class ChunkProviderServerProxy
extends net.minecraft.server.v1_8_R3.ChunkProviderServer
implements Proxy<java.lang.Object>
    A chunk provider server proxy class. To call methods in the base class, call the regular methods. To call methods from the current implementation, call the super_ methods.
